 During the deployment, users carried on their typical daily life.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At the first step, we set the user defined service range as in figure 
\begin_inset LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:User-Defined-RSSI"

\end_inset

.
 Along with the boundaries of the service range, we measured RSSI for among
 all the appliances and tags.
 For the unified threshold technique, we set the RSSI service range as in
 the table 
\begin_inset LatexCommand ref
reference "tab:Unified-and-Calibrated"

\end_inset

 so that both of users can be fairly detected.
 And for the calibrated threshold, we measeared RSSI value at several points
 along the boundaries of the service range, then averaged the values and
 rounded as shown in the table 
\begin_inset LatexCommand ref
reference "tab:Unified-and-Calibrated"

\end_inset

.
 As we mentioned in section 
\begin_inset LatexCommand ref
